<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">She could have gotten the money from anywhere: Mia, her lawyer, a donation from an anonymous sympathizer. It made sense that she had to go back to Chi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">She could have gotten the money from anywhere: Mia, her lawyer, a donation from an anonymous sympathizer. It made sense that she had to go back to China, though. If she stayed in America, she'd be too easily found and her options for getting a job in the US were severely limited. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
