<a href="/questions/1390012-tried-to-read-it-three-separate-times">Tried to read it three separate times. Typical tale about a typical middle class suburb. Zzzzzz.... I&#39;d love to understand why some people liked this book. Reading over the reviews. What was unique?</a>
</div>
